      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 39.8 - 老子 39.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 39.9 - 老子 39.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>其致之，天無以清將恐裂，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>All these are the results of the One (Dao). If heaven were not thus pure, it soon would rend;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
