      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 39.21 - 老子 39.22</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 39.20</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>不欲琭琭如玉，珞珞如石。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>They do not wish to show themselves elegant-looking as jade, but (prefer) to be coarse-looking as an (ordinary) stone.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
